b'Alan Parsons and I are both avocado growers, gentleman farmers, kind of neighbors in agriculture. We met at our mutual friends\xe2\x80\x99 coffee farm and clicked almost immediately, retreating to Alan\xe2\x80\x99s studio to talk music, magic, and cosmos.'
b'...and ultimately become what my own career is about, trying to solve universal quandaries through song craft.'
